    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> This is the eighth month of the Hebrew calendar. It is during the last part of October and the first part of November on Western calendars. (See also: [[
    </div>
    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> “the second year of the reign of Darius the king” or “the second year since Darius became king”
    </div>
