    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> Yahweh speaks of having a change of attitude toward another person as if it were turning or returning. The people turning to Yahweh means that they will again be devoted to him and worship him, while Yahweh returning to the people means that he will again bless them and help them.
