    </div>
    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> There being peace and quiet in the world is spoken of as if the earth were a person who is still and resting. This could mean: (1) this is a good thing that means that there is peace between nations or (2) this is a bad thing that means that there is no war because nations are helpless to fight against a stronger nation that has subdued them.
